column5: The taxes like VAT goes to the country where the turnover comes from. All the wage taxes go to Estonian government.
My company provides all the services you need. I can make the price for 15 eur per month if you do not have transactions and its on standby just in case.
See on sinu oma tõlgendus praegu. Ma ärgitan inimesi mõtlema ja vaatama elule teisiti. Kõik elavad nii nagu tahavad, lihtsalt kõik ei pea ka lubatud ja okei olema. Mõikad?

Igasugused ained, mis on paühhotroopse mõjuga ning illegaalseks peetud, peaksidki jääma selleks. Ega nad seal nimekirjas ilmaasjata pole. Nagu sellest alkoholi ja tubaka tarbimisest meil Eestis veel vähe oleks. Mõni noor nolk arvab, et asi pole nii hull midagi. Ma olen 7 aastat turva olnud ja näinud kõiksugu sitta, mida inimesed nii joobes kui laksu all on võimelised tegema niet siin pole absoluutselt kahtlustki, et narkootikumid peavad jääma illegaalseks. Ma tõstaks alkoholi hinna ka 3kordseks kui saaks. Kas pole elus muud teha kui nädalavahetuseti end pinalisse tõmmata ja järgmine päev peavaluga mööda saata?

Tehke sporti, suhelge inimestega näost näkku, käige matkamas ja reisimas. Vaadake päikseloojangut oma poiss- või tüdruksõbraga.

Ma arvan, et me elame vägagi mõistlikus riigis, kus meil, eestlastel, nuppu jagub ja oleme võimelised end tõestama igal pool. Ärge raisake oma elu mingi mõttetu jamaga tegelemiseks. 

Elu tuleb ise põnevaks teha!
No elu24 “artikkel” ütleb juba kõik.
Kõige ägedam linn maailmas

Kirjavigade pärast vabandan. Ilmselt sai kiiresti tõesti trükitud. Probleem on paljuski kodust tulnu- vanemate ideaal ja ehk ka nende enda napid võimalused minevikus ja üritatakse selle läbi mingit auku täita. Tänapäeval on veelgi raskem tihti leida sihti elus.

-Millist paska?

Suurärimehed on saanud kõike, mida ihaldanud. Tulumaks laekub otse riigile, mitte kohalikku omavalitsusse ja jaotatakse vastavalt rahvaarvule. Teatud piirkonnad ei saagi sellepärast areneda ning maakohad jäävad tühjemaks. Topitakse raha Rail Balticusse, kuid võiks selle asemel teha Eesti infrastruktuuris ümberkorraldusi ning luua meile endile normaalne raudteevõrk, selle asemel, et maanteid lappida ning rekkade teket soodustada. Haridusreform- peaks ammu tehtud olema. Isegi kõrgkoolides õpetatakse sama jura, mida 20 aastat tagasi. Aeg on edasi läinud ning ettevõtja ja haridusasutus ei suuda siiani koostööd teha. Kõrgharidus on tasuta, kuid suures osas kasutu. 

-Kogu Eesti geopoliitiline kurss on vale?

Ei ole kogu kurss vale. Euroopa Liidu liikmena on meile peale surutud kõik võimalikud regulatsioonid. Tegemist ei ole enam ammu majandusliiduga. Me peame kõigi naabritega läbi saama, sest me kõik omamoodi sõltume üksteisest. 

-Riigi seadusandlus ja välispoliitika on mõttetu jama?

Välispoliitika peab olema globaalse suunaga, mitte keskendunud Euroopa Liidule.

Kellele see pensionisüsteem üldse kasulik on? Pensionifonde valitsevad Rootsi pangad, kes teenivad nende pealt isegi siis kui raha kõrbeb. Mina isiklikult pooldan igale kodanikule anda otsuse ise suunata seda pensionifondi nii kuidas soovitakse. See on selge, et noorem põlvkond tasub sotsmaksu ja kuna rahvas on vananev, siis noor generatsioon ise pensioni ei näe, vaid suurt tulumaksuprotsenti tulevikus (sinna ei saa keegi midagi parata). PPA juht ega ka peaprokurör ei tohiks end tunda jumalatena ja öelda välja kõike, mida sülg suhu toob. Käsuliin on käsuliin. Küsimus pole kas avalikult või mitte, vaid selles, millist pilti meedia ise serveerib. Meil puudub objektiivne meedia, selle asemel on hunnik s\*tta tootvaid nn blogijaid.
Nii. Ja mis praegu halvasti siis tehtud? On kelleltki midagi ära võetud või lapsehoolduspuhkus saamata või firmat luua ei saa?

Võiks nagu selle teema lõpetada juba. Mida see Ratas nii halvasti on teinud siis? Ekre ja Isamaa lõhuvad riiki? Reformierakonna paska oleme talunud yle 25 aasta juba, ei ütleks ka, et tarku otsuseid oleks tehtud. Tegelege oma elude parandamisega ise, mitte ärge ajage end närvi mingi mõttetu poliitikajamaga.
Depression is not end of the world. It is just brain chemistry that is little bit out of work, thats it. 20 % of the people in the world has it. It is treatable.

Okay, let me put it this way: how do you deal woth uour depression? Do you use meds? Do you seek proper information or are you trying to help yourself? Do you want to get any help? That also depends on will too. We can all cry here and make ourselves pity here. I want to help myself and I am willing to do anything to resolve my depression. Are you?
Did you tried experiments or solutiouns they offered?
That is your own decision in life. Everyone has the right to choose what to give fuck about. You must be lonely then.
You are most welcome!

Sarah Knight “The life-changing magic of not giving a fuck”- book about how people should care less about everyday bullshit from other people. Why should you stress about your job or people or their opinion about you, when you should only care about your family and friends.

Mark Manson “The subtle art of not giving a fuck”- book about what matters you most in life and how to determine that.


These two books are my official bibles at the moment.

That is good to hear! I myself have got good help with psychiatrist and from pills. I read a lot about depression and also self-help books that really help. There is so much bullshit in some books that is not helpful. It is largely individual too Im sure.
You take pills or not?
You propably asked that stupid question while you were stoned. Why the fuck you need drugs to make yourself feel better?

That is the best decision you have ever made! These sudden moves, when you have had enough and need to take some time off, will end up the best experience and new chances in life. Keep going and showing yourself that life is worth enjoying, not working to death to pay some fucking bills all the time. 

Real proud of you, man!


Sten
Go to a doctor and start curing yourself, end of story.
Ja kui palju see kirumine aitab?
Mis te kirute seda valitsust. Võtke end kokku ja hakake ise tegutsema, et hea elada oleks. Naeruväärne käitumine

What is the problem? Do you have parents or sisters or brothers? Posting something like this is not normal. Do you take medication or havent you been to doctor or something with your problem? There is not any problem you cannot solve in life. Nobody has the right to decide over your life here, so stop posting this stuff.

I agree that you need a purpose. I have found that the best way to feel good and needed isnto help other people: buy a homeless person a sandwich, help elderly people, give some money to somebody who needs it, buy a grocery store cashier a chocolate bar. I try every day to make somebody feel good and that keeps me alive in every way :).
There may be, I do not even argue about it.

I know how they feel, because I feel like this now. I have had depression for 15 years, but lately decided to get help(still wonder how did I lived before). Medication is working. You must get help from doctor, that is good to speak out here and acknowledge the problem to yourself. Also you must change your attitude towards the things that make your illness worse (bad people around you, stressful job etc).

I recommend to read a book that helped me very much.


Sarah Knight “The Life-Changing Magic of Not Giving a F*ck”
:D
Ei koti
Absull ei koti

:D aitäh sulle! Ma pole tükk aega nii korralikult naerda saanud kui praegu. Kohe näha, et sind lausa ajab vihale kõik see, mis toimub ning ajuloputus on sulle hästi mõjunud. Sellist keelekasutust pole ammu näinud, vägev kutt oled!

Aga jh, joo edasi kui raske on taluda mu postitust :)
Kui see sind ei koti, siis miks sa kirjutad siin?
Ilmselgelt mind ei koti, mida sa arvad :)
Ei valinudki kedagi, pole valida

We dont give up to depression, got it? That a**hole can hurt us, not break us!

As you see, even these little things matter to you and gives point to live. I have a suggestion to you for today:


Take a day off and do something you really want or miss. F*ck everything else and other people’s needs and just enjoy that day. Eat a burger, break something, tell somebody annoying peraon to go f*ck themselves, because its your day!


Happy birthday!

Vanemad võiksid aja maha võtta ja tegeleda oma lastega. Võtabki sinise lehe ja tegeleb, midagi teha pole. Lapse tervis on a ja o. Tänapäeva haridussüsteem on läinud ka korralikult julmaks. Eliitkoolides on nõudmised veelgi karmimad ning lapsi õpetatakse nagu roboteid, kes peavad lennult kõike haarama. Küsige oma lastelt, mida nemad teha tahaksid ja andke neile pisut vabadust ning toetage nende valikuid. Küsimus pole laste hinnetes, vaid üleüldises rahulolus. Väga palju määrab sõpruskond, kellega suheldakse, seat kui seal on negatiivseid inimesi, siis on ka laps negatiivne, vihane jne.

Laps peab saama oma vanemaid usaldada, kellele tahetakse muresid kurta. Meie rahvuse kõige haiglasem eripära ongi kõike enda sees hoida ja näha vàlja tugevana, mis tekitab lisastressi.

I think that you are tired of doing things like other people. Every person is different and you should live your life as you want to. Being part of society does not mean that you must be hardworking or too disciplined all the time. Real living consists of soing things that matter to you, not because it is society’s normality. Overreacting is just part of depression, pills can really take care of it. I myself have taken for 4 months now and I feel awesome. Try to change your attitude towards other people and your daily life. 

Everyone who suffers from depression should read this book:

“The Life-Changing Magic of Not Giving A F*Ck” by Sarah Knight

https://www.amazon.com/Life-Changing-Magic-Not-Giving-Spending/dp/0316270725/ref=mp_s_a_1_4?keywords=sarah+knight&qid=1562222459&s=gateway&sr=8-4


This book is my bible doing everyday activities. I strongly recommend you all to read and analyze your everyday life.
Great seeing that you are an active person all the time! What other projects you have you planned for future? Re5pect

Everyone must have felt it. Most of the people in this world do not know exactly what kind of profession they might want or what are they good at. I myself have made this through and finally realized what I want. First of all, stop worrying all the time about the job. In your earlier post you mentioned that you live in your aunts trailer or sth and she is psychotic. Take your main goal here: moving out. You do not need a car, why do you want to raise your expenses by that? You and your girlfriend have each other, that is the most important thing.

If you cant hold on to your job more than few months or so, you have to create your own job (company or sth) and start doing what you love!

Listen to me. Have you been to a psychiatrist with your problems? First you need to get medicine. Secondly you have to keep in touch with the people who care about you and tell “fuck off” to the people who do not deserve you or do not care about you. A parent who abandons their children are just cowards and low-life piece of shits. Sometimes things wont go as we want, thats called life. I myself have gotten much help with doctors and I have made my environment suitable for me and I will keep telling people to “F off” until I am satisfied with my surroundings. Keep your head up, mate! Life is better than you see at the moment. This is serious condition and the pill does work. Doing yoga or meditation does not help with your condition, thats for sure.

You can write to me personally if you need support or help, I can gladly guide you!

Coop pank on väga mõnus pank. Sulli saab igal pool üle Eesti välja võtta, teenindus siga hea. Kaart töötab laitmatult. Tavalisest pangast àrge otsiga head intressi. ERIAL hoiustes korralik intress, mul endal kasvab vara seal.

Miks sellist jama üldse postitada? Ärge jälgige seda solgitud jama, mida nimetatakse meediaks. Ilma “uudiseid” vaatamata ja lugemata saab palju mõnusamalt elada. See solk, mida kokku kirjutatakse peabki intrigeeriv meie jaoks olema, sest siis oleme vihased ja emotsionaalsed asjade suhtes, mis meid kottima ei peaks. Ei erine see lääne meedia ida omast üldse. Loobuge oma aju mürgitamisest ja hakake tegelema asjadega, mis teile korda lähevad!
Tundub, et soomlaste jaoks on ka alkohol kõige tähtsam
Pole ühtki valitsust, kellega eestlane rahul oleks. Kandideeri Riigikokku ja hakka ise asja ajama kui ideid ja hakkamist on. Mingite tobedate piltide tegemine ja postitamine ei muuda mitte midagi.

You have a reason to live in this world, try to think little bit more positively. I have felt the same feelings. Try not to care about the things that do not matter to you or you cant control. In the last 2 months I do not give a fuck about the things I cannot control (besides my depression) and started living for myself. I feel so much better now and I am trying to help others with these problems. Take a vacation from everything that annoys or is disturbing you and see that life is great!
Life is not pointless, our thoughts that we cannot control are. Take a deep breath and do something radical for a change. Do something good to somebody everyday, that gives the point.
